<h3 id="orga82dd0f">Vega <span class="timestamp-wrapper"><span class="timestamp">[2021-10-15 Fri]</span></span></h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-orga82dd0f">

<div id="org6e5850d" class="figure">
