<p>
What do you do from morning to night?<br />
I endure myself.
</p>
</blockquote>

<blockquote>
<p>
Knowledge subverts love: in proportion as we penetrate our secrets, we come to loathe our kind, precisely because they resemble us. 
</p>
</blockquote>

